short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Switch URL for Google Workspace services

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Simplifies operation of Google Docs, Google Spreadsheet, Google Slides, and Google Forms.
Right-click or pop-up to launch a new Google Doc or view Google Slides in preview mode.

Details of functions
・Create new pages (Docs, Slides, SpreadSheet, Forms)
・Change status (Edit mode, View mode, Copy, Template)
・Create download links (pdf, docx, xlsx, pptx, csv)

It increases the productivity of people who use Google products.
